    <script type="text/javascript">
     $(document).ready(function () {
                var slide = $('.featuredStory > .content');
                //slide.on("initialized.owl.carousel translated.owl.carousel", function (e) {
                //    updateBackgroundImage();
                //});
                slide.owlCarousel({
                    
                    responsive: {
                        0: {
                            mouseDrag: true,
                            items: 1,
                            slideBy: 1,
                            autoplay: false,
                        },
                        1024: {
                            mouseDrag: false,
                            items: 2,
                            slideBy: 2,
                            autoplay: false,
                        }
                    },
                    nav: true,
                    smartSpeed: 1800,
                    navContainer: '.featuredStory .customNav',
                    dotsContainer: '.featuredStory .customDot',
                    //onInitialize: resizeSlider,
                });

                var triggerTarget = null;
                $(".featuredStory .owl-item").click(function (e) {
                    if (!$(e.target).is("a")) {
                        tiggerTarget = null;
                        var target = $(e.target);
                        if (!target.hasClass("owl-item")) {
                            target = target.parents(".owl-item");
                        }
                        var link = target.find("div.title > a");
                        if (link != undefined && link != null) {
                            link.trigger('click');
                        }
                    } else if ($(e.target).is("a") && e.target != triggerTarget) {
                        triggerTarget = e.target;
                        var target = $(e.target);
                        if (!target.hasClass("youtube")) {
                            target[0].click();
                        }
                    }
                });

                $(".featuredStory .youtube").each(function () {
                    var videourl = $(this).attr("data-video-url");
                    videourl = videourl.replace(/https?:(.*)/gi, '$1');
                    $(this).attr("data-lity", "");
                    $(this).attr("data-lity-target", videourl);

   <script language="javascript">
    $(document).ready(function () {
        $("a.email[href^=mailto]").each(function () {
            $(this).click(function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                var email = $(this).attr("href");
                showDisclaimer(email);
            });
        });
    });

    function showDisclaimer(address) {
        $(".acceptContainer a").attr("href", address);
        ConfigSizeAndLocation();
    }

    function ConfigSizeAndLocation() {
        $(".disclaimerBackground").fadeIn();
        var currentWidth = $(window).width();
        var winWidth = currentWidth;
       
        if (currentWidth <= 700) {
            $(".disclaimerContainer").width(currentWidth - 100);
            winWidth = (winWidth / 2) - $(".disclaimerContainer").outerWidth(true) / 2;
            $(".disclaimerContainer").css("left", winWidth);
        } else {
            $(".disclaimerContainer").css("width", "");
            winWidth = (winWidth / 2) - $(".disclaimerContainer").outerWidth(true) / 2;
            $(".disclaimerContainer").css("left", winWidth);
        }

        $(".disclaimerContainer").fadeIn();

        $(window).resize(function () {
            if ($(this).width() != currentWidth) {
                currentWidth = $(this).width();
                winWidth = currentWidth;
                winWidth = (winWidth / 2) - 287;
                $(".disclaimerContainer").css("left", winWidth);
            }
        });
    }

    function hideDisclaimer() {
        $(".disclaimerContainer").fadeOut();
        $(".disclaimerBackground").fadeOut();
    }
   </script>
   <style type="text/css">
    .disclaimerBackground { display: none; position: fixed; width: 100%; height: 100%; top: 0; left: 0; z-index: 100; background-color: #404040; opacity: 0.7; filter: alpha(opacity=70); }
    .disclaimerContainer { display: none; position: fixed; width: 574px; top: 80px; top: 5vh; left: 200px; max-height:85vh; background-color: #d0d4d6; z-index: 130; padding: 22px; }
    .disclaimerContainer .subheader1 { margin-bottom: 22px; }
    .disclaimerContainer .bodyintro { font-size: 17px; }
    .disclaimerContainer .normalbodytext { padding-top: 0; }
    .disclaimerContainer .disclaimerAD { float: right; margin-top: 18px; margin-right: 18px; }
    .disclaimerContainer .disclaimerAD .acceptContainer { float: left; }
    .disclaimerContainer .disclaimerAD .declineContainer { float: left; margin-left: 18px; }
